                        <interp inst="t18681123-name-175" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD STIGGLES</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman C R</hi> 23). On 7th November, about 9.30, I met the last witness in Newport Market—he pointed out the prisoner to me, and charged him with assaulting him with some instrument—the prisoner made no answer at all.</p>
